messages.message:
Hi all --

We are consolidating our SQL database tech for AI Hub. Relevant deadlines:
1. Migration of SaaS stacks from MySQL to PostgreSQL *starts at the end of Q3.*
2. Deadline for migration of VPC stacks to PostgreSQL is *April 2026.*
More details are in this document. (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sH2MexeY506HY2yeTIU6KvWVj1lPncY_GS5xIhtMYQE/edit?usp=sharing) Thank you!
